Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}六月2日 Goinia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的方式奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了誰 搞的我落到現在這個處境？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miguel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不如早點開槍...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不知情的家伙在場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射殺嫌疑犯是需要理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的是她沒有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那槍里沒有上子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和孩子沒有關系吧 你們能接管她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不管你了 而是想設法一起過關
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:01:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上我就會去接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi怎么辦？ 我們不是要一起去見他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才到了這里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 我見到Hiroshi了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己最重要的人都無法保護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是那種軟弱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！ 你們快過來幫忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點放開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 快點逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！ 站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 快點上車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓她們逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有亂來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還早10年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彎腰 Hathin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}嫌疑犯正沿著Macro大街逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓活得 我要親手做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的槍在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就去找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在嫌疑犯后方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從正面過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標已經捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你在哪里見到的？ Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他又在打算逃跑 那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出來吧臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯Michiko Malandro雖然企圖逃跑...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是所有問題都被我搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲的只是一個年幼的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人射一發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！ 快追！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來接管Michiko Malandro的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經通知過你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒我想聽聽游樂場事件相關人員和隊員的詳細證詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Michiko Malandro吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回Diamandra監獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricardo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有忘記我啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭發變長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在追你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這句嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我該怎么辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 你的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 可以把門打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點鐘啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 希望你能飛一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到天亮為止你們就等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起吃飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就過來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin你也要吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以叫你Hatchin嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會做飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會啊 理所當然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒見你做過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽子那么小 會被嚇死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:11:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么打算的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 等把一切都做給了斷之后我就去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 就微笑著說再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi 和這個家伙在一起一定會變得有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 既然你這么說 那準沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 微笑著 說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機身會搖晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加10個pastel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上9點到晚上8點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我每天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄件人不明的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經是第6個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個包裹寄到是1周前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常華麗的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惡心了 而且我也穿不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么這么大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾有假期的時候就這樣和孩子一起度過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孩子的父親3個月就分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道是像誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常... 非常...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野蠻 讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的時候 有事突然會感到孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}長達數月的逃亡生活終于畫上了句號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Michiko Malandro嫌疑犯居然自首了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}當局將加強對其的監管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}對其在逃亡過程中所犯的罪行也會進行追究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿越國境了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們填補空白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長達10年的巨大空白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為希望而興奮 大談家族之愛的這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果和新認識的女人一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我的心最初就不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像空殼一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一時心血來潮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給Michiko寫了封信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到回信是過了一段日子之后了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"查無此人"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常粗暴的字體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗暴的字體？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗暴... 的..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是通向我家的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體如同被電一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這條路的遠處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們的旅途會到什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
